CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 30, 1958, pg. 32 reads: "Senior Ladies - Only three ladies are taking part in senior division of the UGA Women's Division. They are, left to right: Mrs. Adelaide Adams, Washington, D.C.; Mrs. Rhoda Finger Fowler, New York City, and Mrs. Helen Harris, Washington, D.C., defending champion."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of golfers Adelaide Adams, Rhoda Finger Fowler, and Helen Harris, standing against metal fence with brick wall, North Park golf course for UGA tournament
